PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of JEAN-LOUIS HAMEL, of Verdun, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of VIA Rail Canada Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Michel Biron, who has resigned.
